message.name: INF_INSLINEITEM_REASONTEXT_MULTEMPL
message.locale: The period specified %1s for the contribution matches more than one known employment for the Person %2s employed by %3s. Please investigate to which employment the contribution belongs.

message.name: INF_INSLINEITEM_REASONTEXT_OVERLAPEMPL

message.name: INF_INSLINEITEM_SUBJECTTEXT_OVERLAPEMPL
